---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="section-padding bg-surface relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 surface-grain pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="container-custom relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 lg:gap-24 items-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">
          <span class="eyebrow-number">02 / Nosotros</span>
          <span class="section-eyebrow-line"></span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="display-2 text-balance mb-8">
          Una historia de
          <span class="display-italic text-gradient-warm">100.000 oficios</span>
          aprendidos.
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-ink-muted leading-relaxed max-w-prose">
          <p class="text-[1.05rem]">
            Instituto Celsius nació en 2006 con una misión clara: <strong class="text-ink font-medium">democratizar el acceso a la formación profesional</strong> en Mendoza y, después, en toda Argentina a través de nuestras aulas virtuales.
          </p>
          <p>
            Combinamos teoría rigurosa y práctica intensiva. Nuestros programas se diseñan junto a referentes activos de cada industria, para que lo que aprendés esté al día con lo que se pide hoy en el mercado.
          </p>
          <p>
            Modalidad presencial en nuestra sede, o cursada 100% online con tutores reales. Vos elegís el ritmo; nosotros sostenemos el rigor.
          </p>
        </div>

        <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-10 max-w-lg">
          {[
            'Planes actualizados cada ciclo',
            'Material descargable de por vida',
            'Pagos en cuotas sin interés',
            'Bolsa de trabajo activa',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[0.92rem] text-ink">
              <span class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-tint border border-brand/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                <Icon name="lucide:check" class="w-3 h-3 text-brand-deep" />
              </span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="relative reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-ink via-brand-deep to-brand p-7 flex flex-col justify-between text-white relative overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.06] bg-dot-grid bg-[length:14px_14px]"></div>
              <div class="relative">
                <p class="text-eyebrow uppercase text-white/60">Desde</p>
                <p class="font-display text-[3.5rem] leading-none mt-2">2006</p>
              </div>
              <div class="relative">
                <p class="font-display text-xl leading-tight tracking-tight">
                  18 años formando<br/>
                  <span class="display-italic text-warm-light">en oficios</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="aspect-square rounded-3xl bg-warm-tint border border-warm/15 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
              <Icon name="lucide:award" class="w-7 h-7 text-warm-deep" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-display text-3xl text-warm-deep leading-none tracking-tight">50<span class="text-warm">+</span></p>
                <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1.5">cursos activos por ciclo</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 pt-12">
            <div class="aspect-square rounded-3xl bg-surface-raised border border-hairline p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
              <div class="flex -space-x-2">
                {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map((i) => (
                  <div class={`w-9 h-9 rounded-full border-2 border-surface-raised flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-medium ${
                    i === 1 ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-brand to-brand-deep' :
                    i === 2 ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-warm to-warm-deep' :
                    i === 3 ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-emerald-700' :
                    i === 4 ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-amber-700' :
                    'bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-500 to-rose-700'
                  }`}>{['M','D','L','C','A'][i-1]}</div>
                ))}
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-display text-3xl text-ink leading-none tracking-tight">+500</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1.5">alumnos cada mes</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-3xl bg-surface-raised border border-hairline p-7 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden group">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_30%,rgba(217,119,87,0.15),transparent_50%)] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
              <div class="relative">
                <p class="text-eyebrow uppercase text-ink-subtle">Valoración</p>
                <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mt-2">
                  <p class="font-display text-[3.5rem] leading-none text-ink">4.8</p>
                  <Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-5 h-5 text-warm fill-warm" />
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-0.5 mt-2">
                  {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => <Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-3 h-3 text-warm fill-warm" />)}
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="relative">
                <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-tight">
                  Promedio en Google Maps<br/>
                  sobre <strong class="text-ink font-medium">247 reseñas</strong>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
